intent_execution_notes:
intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_1: "Worn untucked over high-rise slim or straight bottoms. Fitted knit body provides vertical body engagement; waist-length hem creates a minor horizontal break at the natural waist but the overall read is body-following column. Partial Intent 1 — works for users who accept some waist visibility within a fitted register.",

  intent_2: "Worn untucked at waist-length, the waist-length hem at the waist, or a tuck into the high-rise, is the waist she makes. Pair with high-rise fitted bottom for the hourglass uniform; the meeting point of top hem and high rise reveals the waist. styling_anchor strategy by construction. Strong Intent 2 match for hourglass (natural shape confirmation) and lean rectangle (waist creation via length)."
}

