intent_execution_notes:
intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_1: "Worn over fitted close/tight bottom. Body engaged throughout, deep V with lace trim reinforces vertical line through the upper body. Waist-length hem ends at the natural waist but isn't a styling event — the garment is too short to tuck. The result is a fitted vertical silhouette with featured upper body (décolletage, bust, shoulders, arms via sleeveless)."
}

