intent_execution_notes:
intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_6: "Worn untucked over relaxed or slim bottoms (cropped trousers, wide-leg, dark denim). Oversized cotton + drop-shoulder + hip-length + neutral strategy = body not engaged. The lace peek hem provides a feminine surprise detail that distinguishes this from a pure basic tee, while remaining in step-back register. Hero of urban_ease outfits where contemporary oversized silhouette is the visual story."
}

