    ]
  }
]

intent_execution_notes:
intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_2: "Worn with fitted top tucked into the high-rise. The tuck + visible high waistband + fitted seat creates a deliberate waist event. styling_anchor strategy. Fires for users who commit to the technique — Q5a = tuck, accepts high-rise + wide-leg + the fitted-at-seat construction. The user is creating a waist visually through styling, regardless of whether she explicitly featured waist in Q3.",

  intent_4: "Same wearing pattern (fitted top tucked into high-rise) but the user has also named hips/curves OR seat as featuring zones. The fitted seat + wide leg from thigh adds proportion contrast that celebrates the small-waist-to-fuller-bottom differential. Fires additively on top of Intent 2 for users in curve-celebration mode."
}

