intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_1: "Worn with fitted top untucked over the mid-rise. The close fit through hip + seat + straight leg gives a body-traced column from waist down. Paired with fitted top, the silhouette is vertical throughout with no waist break. Classic Intent 1 base layer for fitted-throughout outfits.",

  intent_2: "Tucked or half-tucked into the mid-rise. The fitted seat + visible mid-rise waistband creates the waist event at the meeting point. styling_anchor strategy. Smoke-and-mirrors waist creation for users who commit to the tuck technique."
}

intent_execution_notes: {
  intent_1: "Worn with fitted top untucked over the high-rise waistband. The close fit through hip + seat + straight leg gives a body-traced column from waist to ankle. Paired with a fitted top falling at hip-length, the silhouette is a clean vertical line. Stronger Intent 1 execution than mid-rise versions because the high rise extends body engagement higher into the natural waist area.",

  intent_2: "Tucked or half-tucked into the high-rise waistband. The high waistband sits at the natural waist creating a visible, strong waist event at the meeting point with the fitted tucked top. styling_anchor strategy. The high rise specifically optimizes Intent 2 — the waistband is at the most prominent natural waist position, making the meeting point the visual headline of the outfit. Smoke-and-mirrors waist creation at maximum effectiveness."
}

